column1: Weighted MRI size (256, 256, 1) in T2, exhibiting the head of a man of 37 years old, of coronal section n°109 starting from the back of the skull. We see clearly: the white matter of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 591.9434 mm³, the cortex of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 1761.3281 mm³, the white matter of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 747.5098 mm³ and the cortex of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 1890.5273 mm³.
